# CaretTab
CaretTab is a simple New Tab page replacement for Google Chrome.

## We've moved!
The official page for the CaretTab New Tab extension has been moved. Please visit us at [http://bluecaret.com/project/carettab](http://bluecaret.com/project/carettab) instead. Thank you!
